<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:13:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中美在日内瓦会面讨论人工智能风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</link><description>美国官员表示，美国和中国将于周二在日内瓦举行会议，讨论先进人工智能问题，并强调，即使会谈探讨减轻新兴技术带来的风险，华盛顿的政策也不会进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-china-meet-geneva-discuss-ai-risks-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：拜登新关税对中国的打击有多大？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>据知情人士透露，美国总统乔·拜登最快将于周二宣布对中国征收新关税，目标包括电动汽车、医疗用品和太阳能设备等行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/how-hard-will-new-biden-tariffs-hit-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>德国称 2023 年外国行为者实施的网络犯罪增加了 28%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</link><description>周一公布的数据显示，2023 年德国外国犯罪者的网络犯罪激增，较上年增长 28%，而欧洲在选举前夕对涉嫌俄罗斯黑客和间谍的担忧加剧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-cybercrime-by-foreign-actors-rose-by-28-2023-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>英国警方指控三名男子协助香港外国情报部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</link><description>英国警方周一表示，当局在英格兰各地进行了一系列逮捕行动后，三名男子被指控协助香港外国情报部门。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 07:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>日本软银转向季度盈利，关注 Arm 部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/softbank-swings-q4-profit-21-bln-2024-05-13/</link><description>科技投资者软银集团周一表示，该公司在本财年最后一个季度实现净利润，这家日本巨头专注于人工智能，以帮助推动经济恢复增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/softbank-swings-q4-profit-21-bln-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司的亏损表明其难以填补欧盟与中国的天然气销售缺口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-loss-shows-struggle-fill-eu-gas-sales-gap-with-china-2024-05-13/</link><description>克里姆林宫旗下的能源巨头俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司（Gazprom）曾经是俄罗斯最赚钱的公司，但由于其国内市场和中国出口难以填补欧洲天然气销售损失的缺口，该公司可能会面临长期业绩不佳的局面。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 06:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/gazprom-loss-shows-struggle-fill-eu-gas-sales-gap-with-china-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>WPIC 表示，供应疲软将导致 2024 年铂金缺口高于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weaker-supply-will-drive-platinum-deficit-higher-than-expected-2024-wpic-says-2024-05-13/</link><description>世界铂金投资理事会 (WPIC) 周一表示，由于南非和俄罗斯矿山供应减少，2024 年全球铂金短缺将比此前预期更深。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:10:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weaker-supply-will-drive-platinum-deficit-higher-than-expected-2024-wpic-says-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着美国通货膨胀，每一位小数都很重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-05-13/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 05:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，菲律宾海岸警卫队将阻止中国在争议浅滩进行填海造地活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-coast-guard-wont-allow-china-reclamation-disputed-shoal-official-says-2024-05-13/</link><description>菲律宾海岸警卫队（PCG）发言人周一表示，菲律宾海岸警卫队致力于维持在南海争议地区的存在，以确保中国不会在萨比纳浅滩进行填海造地活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 03:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-coast-guard-wont-allow-china-reclamation-disputed-shoal-official-says-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国求助于米利西奇以恢复钢玫瑰的命运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-turn-milicic-restore-fortunes-steel-roses-2024-05-13/</link><description>中国要求安特·米利西奇扭转女足国家队的命运，并在周末任命这位 50 岁的澳大利亚人为水青霞的接班人。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-turn-milicic-restore-fortunes-steel-roses-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>通胀严重的一周股市逼近历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-13/</link><description>全球股市周一接近历史新高，本周通胀数据可能影响或打破美国早些时候降息的预期，而中国的经济活动数据将考验人们对世界第二大经济体持续复苏的乐观情绪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 01:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国电商巨头面临折扣与利润之间的微妙平衡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-e-commerce-giants-face-delicate-balance-between-discounts-profit-2024-05-12/</link><description>中国电子商务巨头阿里巴巴和京东本周发布的季度收益报告将受到密切关注，作为世界第二大经济体消费者情绪的晴雨表。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 23:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-e-commerce-giants-face-delicate-balance-between-discounts-profit-2024-05-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Shein 在美国上市遇到障碍的情况下加紧伦敦 IPO 准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>消息人士称，如果此次IPO成功，可能会成为今年全球规模最大的IPO之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>